":0.0,"bundleId":"com.go-tellm.tellm","genreIds":["6005","6009"],"primaryGenreName":"Social Networking","primaryGenreId":6005,"releaseDate":"2014-06-15T00:49:30Z","trackName":"Jodel: Hyperlocal Community","trackId":789870026,"sellerName":"The Jodel Venture GmbH","isVppDeviceBasedLicensingEnabled":true,"currentVersionReleaseDate":"2026-04-09T09:04:41Z","releaseNotes":"We've fixed some bugs and made some general improvements.","version":"7.179","wrapperType":"software","currency":"NOK","description":"With Jodel, you can stay connected with the people around you and discover what’s happening in your local area in real time. Whether it’s news, questions, events, confessions, or just a good laugh – you'll never miss out on what's happening around you again! A community app where what you say matters.\n\n[Stay informed & enjoy real moments]\nGet the latest local news and updates instantly in your real time feed – Jodel is full of creativity, humor, and unexpected fun. Unlike traditional social media, Jodel keeps things real and focused on your local life and interests.\n\n[Join the conversation]\nAsk people near you questions, share insights, and get real answers while exploring channels and communities based on your interests. Whether you’re a student at university or college, new to a neighbourhood or just looking to make friends and meet like-minded people – Jodel and its hyperlocal community is the place for you. With your vote on a Jodel post you can decide what's trending in your connected community.\n\n[Connect with locals]\nInteract with others around you through your Jodel posts. Whether you're discussing campus life & college experiences, upcoming events, local news, or general life situations, Jodel helps you stay engaged in your community.\n\n\nWith Jodel you can...\n*be yourself without social pressure\n*share posts, pictures and videos with everyone around you\n*add multiple replies to your post while creating it to write stories without interruptions\n*vote and react on posts and decide what is relevant in your area\n*pin content you want to follow\n*join channels with content that interests you\n*collect Karma by spreading good vibes\n\n\nShare your personal stories with your Jodel friends! Be your original and unique self, share your own amazing thoughts, connect, and make friends. And by the way...Jodel is pronounced \"YODEL\"!\n\nJodel is not just your basic social media. Jodel is...\n\nHYPERLOCAL – Stay updated on everything happening near you.\nDIVERSE & ENGAGING – Meet new people and share your thoughts.\nSUPPORTIVE & FRIENDLY – A positive community with space for everyone.\n\nDownload Jodel now and become part of the most vibrant social hub in your city. Discover the latest news, and engage with your community like never before.\n\n\nhttps://jodel.com/","contentAdvisoryRating":"17+","trackCensoredName":"Jodel: Hyperlocal Community","trackViewUrl":"https://apps.apple.com/no/app/jodel-hyperlocal-community/id789870026?uo=4","averageUserRating":4.1302,"artistId":789870029,"artistName":"The Jodel Venture GmbH","userRatingCount":11874}